    <note type="biography">
        <p>Spanish-born theological writer. Ordained priest, 1798. Left for England in 1810, as the French advanced into Spain. Published a monthly periodical called <hi rend="italic">El Español</hi>, 1810–14. Ordained in the Anglican Church, 1814. Formed a close friendship with Richard Whately at Oxford, joining him in Dublin in 1832.</p></note>
